{"tid":393552,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"請聲稱反5毛的 未來撚呀廢 幫手推post","createTime":"2017-09-09T10:47:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-02T09:15:05.000Z","uid":54373,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"61e2844bfda947a0fe8eb115dbb7fbe5570ba339","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:47:07.000Z","msg":"我真係未見過你<br />\n<br />\n-屌習近平<br />\n-撐劉曉波<br />\n-回應郭文貴<br />\n-關注支爆<br />\n-黃之鋒坐監<br />\n<br />\n屌，真係多到數唔晒<br />\n<br />\n各位巴打可用起底功能觀賞觀賞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/09/184419_036db12a322798c1898f4f45969a1d5d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F09%2F184419_036db12a322798c1898f4f45969a1d5d.jpg&h=17b482d9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c28aa2bcbc392731d2c4600e218d7f139a9a290d","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:48:22.000Z","msg":"有凡事講求證據<br />\n唔係你搖旗納喊反5毛就洗到底<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行為比口講重要</span><br />\n<br />\n-從來唔敢侮辱支那<br />\n-從來唔敢討論郭文貴爆料 and中共權鬥<br />\n-屌2句禮義廉，就話自己反5毛<br />\n-反佢就係5毛<br />\n<br />\n事實勝於雄辯，出返幾個post咀咒支那滅國都未試過，追擊你可疑性就話我係5毛？ <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">估中既內容，全部都係中聯辦會知道晒既野</span><br />\n<br />\n1. 特狗票數<br />\n(中聯辦 基本神早知道晒所有共匪投票意向，如過真是未來來，點會記唔到咁好記的777 no.，因為當時中聯辦都怕有游離票。)<br />\n2.波叔財爺<br />\n3.歌女做唔到教育局<br />\n<br />\n呢3樣如果佢係中聯辦特派，知道並不難。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n之後其他爆料又9吹幾年後，無可能短期實現既事<br />\n什麼北泡，侵侵連任，呢d無5年都證實唔到<br />\n<br />\n而我及各巴打比佢既問題佢一概不答，有留意我追擊佢既問題都簡單合情合理，未來撚無可能不識。<br />\n<br />\n懷疑佢的疑點好合理<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n引申1<br />\n佢每次技窮，都會搬出對方是5毛，之後轉移視線<br />\n唔答人野，大家活係 高/連登 多年，邊班人長期掛對方是5毛係口邊，大家都明。<br />\n<br />\n引申2<br />\n仲有，佢自稱反5毛，真係有出過幾個post<br />\n不過對抗大量5毛既 郭文貴post，真係未見過佢囉<br />\n講句支那都唔敢<br />\n<br />\n引申3<br />\n巴打問親支那會唔會收皮既問題，一概不答。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我會繼續update<br />\n我不介意被人說是5毛，因為唔係唔會你講2句就會係<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">行為比口講重要</span>"},{"pid":"61791209d85b43bc0323c8da4eeeda7d8d96d744","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T10:50:45.000Z","msg":"張習總圖<br />\n真係萬試萬靈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8bc29ff00fa82735137ad5f2609a5a027dbd76a7","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:02:26.000Z","msg":"15分鐘未肯入來<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"97c1f1e23cbc3306613df75a09d54b92202c81bc","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T11:13:46.000Z","msg":"30分鐘未見 呀廢<br />\n<br />\n惡靈既散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/09/191344_408084e96d138c3d1f643eb305799aac.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F09%2F191344_408084e96d138c3d1f643eb305799aac.jpg&h=dad27fec&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"f65ec0c4b73ce6123d09d4c65da8959513bd9b8a","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:16:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ee1b30e2a90da29e55bd9dfbd5f20010a141baf","tid":393552,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-09T12:22:38.000Z","msg":"嘩 真係 惡靈退散<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8e67edaecf7c43d